			<div class="content" id="post-content-1443230">
									

<p>I upvoted at:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>The officer on the security cameras for that area took almost no notice, logging only “Doctors passed, injured.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Aside from being a very well-executed character study of Gears this piece also documents the insanity that being in the business of containing and studying SCPs brings with it without resorting to LOLFoundation reports of whacky antics and suicide watches. This one line tells me so much more about the general apathy creep, the emotionally blunting effect of being exposed to a truth that does not belong in a rational worldview.</p>
<p>Bravo.</p>

